sentence: please list the flights from memphis to new york city on a monday night
sq2:
SELECT DISTINCT  '"'||v0.flight_id||'"', '"'||v1.airport_code||'"',
 '"'||v2.city_code||'"', '"'||v2.city_name||'"', '"'||v3.airport_code||'"',
 '"'||v4.city_code||'"', '"'||v4.city_name||'"',
 '"'||v0.flight_days||'"', v0.departure_time FROM flight v0,
 airport_service v1, city v2, airport_service v3, city v4 
WHERE (((v0.from_airport = ANY v1.airport_code) AND ((v1.city_code = ANY v2.city_code) 
AND (v2.city_name = 'MEMPHIS'))) 
AND (((v0.to_airport = ANY v3.airport_code) AND ((v3.city_code = ANY v4.city_code) 
AND (v4.city_name = 'NEW YORK'))) 
AND (((v0.flight_days IN (
SELECT v5.days_code FROM days v5 
WHERE (v5.day_name = 'MONDAY'))) AND ((v0.departure_time >=  1800) 
AND (v0.departure_time <=  2400))) OR ((v0.flight_days IN (
SELECT v6.days_code FROM days v6 
WHERE (v6.day_name = 'TUESDAY'))) 
AND (v0.departure_time <=  600)))));
